Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:55.91,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,10,,{\i1}Honto no yuki misete kuretara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:55.91,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Si me muestras tu verdadero valor{\i0}
